Create a login and password checking program:
1) Checking if it is a real E-mail address:
- contains a symbol '@' and a '.' after '@';
- no digits after '.';
2) Checking a valid password:
 - not shorter than 8 symbols;
 - contains at least 1 digit;
 - contains at least 1 special symbol;
 - contains at least 1 uppercase letter;
 - contains at least 1 lowercase letter.